title: [FSX/P3D] Ants Airplanes Sierra LSA v1.41
description:
This is the latest version of Ant's Airplanes Sierra LSA for you guys.

This has been patched to the latest version for you guys and does NOT require any further patching at the moment.

Remove the old shortcuts from your Start menu BEFORE installing this to prevent duplicate shortcuts. As far as I know this can be installed on top of the old version, but a clean install is RECOMMENDED as always.

This is still a nice plane, but it is starting to show its age now.

Please SEED this package if you like it; I can't seed everything forever!

Enjoy!
